Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很危险 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,突破各种艰难的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,两位年轻有为的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,成为守护这颗星球的绯红守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一人 结人皇上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,另一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧卡门上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在令人值得纪念的出关仪式前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,两名备受注目的怪伐军\N即将展现他们的实力…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的话…太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 认输吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有机可趁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(闹钟)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,(入伍仪式开始时间紧迫)\N(动作快)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,(危险区域 禁止进入)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是今天加入绯红守护者的\N那歧卡门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是这个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,下则报导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,(备受注目 第567届新队员)\N今天即将举办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(备受注目 第567届新队员)\N本年度怪伐军入伍仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,加入怪伐军的均是通过\N严苛SAS适性测试的菁英们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在此介绍今年的候选明星队员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要介绍我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(辉煌的家世 志愿入怪伐军)\N结人皇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现今新日向国评议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-条皇先生的儿子\N-果然是介绍你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,(条皇 评议会议长)\N没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,(条皇 评议会议长)\N其祖先是建国之父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,辉煌家族的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(界人皇 怪伐军本部长)\N其兄长界人煌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是新日向怪伐军的本部长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他放弃从政 投身到前线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,另外还有个令人在意的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,根据相关人士的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,听说结人的超脑力适性较低
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,养尊处优的少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是否能耐得住与怪异艰辛的战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-感觉好差\N-下则报导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,结人 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脑力值较低 是事实嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不管谁说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天起你就是怪伐军了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你 都是为了这天而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,当上怪伐军\N是你从小梦寐以求的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你可要铭记在心喔 结人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(警报)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怪异警报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然在欢天喜庆的日子搅局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,发布怪异警报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,各地的确切出现机率如下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一击消灭怪异的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,荣获七剑星一等勋章的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(卡连崔佛斯少将 超脑力：噬脑者)\N噬脑者 卡莲崔佛斯少将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是诗宾少将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,(吹雪诗宾少将 超脑力：冷却)\N他冻结了怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,吹雪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也得像他们那样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你要…活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,《绯红结系》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现实的Crimｅ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For Heaven's sake
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接受虚假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,永恒的幻想 层层逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,绝非完美 I get sick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,转身而来的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在这瞬息世界中 落下了奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit the venom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know why
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 绝顶的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Criminal gets life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been in love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我何时开始厌倦了这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday I won't be crying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不再伤害 而牺牲了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(绯红的超脑力)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真幸运 这样就不算迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是在等卡莲队长他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原来同期里有这么可爱的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,直见兰德尔 直见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,旁边的是妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,她们的年纪相同耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是双胞胎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她在看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,姊姊 不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,随便露出破绽\N很容易被那种人缠上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,重 妳总是把我当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我看的是旁边那位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,界人皇本部长的训示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,全体 起立
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的哥哥耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有高洁志向之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,才能被选进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我为各位的勇气及热情\N由衷地感到敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然而在这频繁受到\N怪异威胁的国家中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天生拥有优秀超脑力之人的招募组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,及藉由锻炼提升脑力的志愿组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力)\N不分彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如不结合各自的脑力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,便无法越过重重难关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现如今只知道\N怪异来自平流层的断绝之带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,其他仍有许多未解之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 拥有对付怪异能力的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正是防御的重要基石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在执行任务的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也别忘了今日心中的抱负
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,从此刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,共2168的诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,便是新日向国怪伐军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,绯红守护者的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(那歧 卡门)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,(结人 皇)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想跟直见搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被人救的时候 你几岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,五岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当时在怪伐军里的女性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,直见兰德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟然在找这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,名门贵族兰德尔家的长女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在她身边的是妹妹 重兰德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,重小时候 双亲被怪异所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,之后被兰德尔家收养
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,与同年龄的直见成为姊妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,12岁时被招募进怪伐军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是训练时期的榜首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,直见是第五名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她们是菁英姐妹花嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,重 兰德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德尔家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得在父亲的就职庆祝会上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没看到救你的人的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不过结人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我得先说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你追重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然她看起来很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而我追直见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 重还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今天早上妳说\N又做了"红色系线之梦"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,别放开…别解开红色系线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,跟妳的超脑力有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 我更担心姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是否能编列在同一队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,姊姊个性较笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得保护妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,重 妳好过分喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不知道究竟是谁救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟连大哥都不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,结人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们分到同一队了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,花火 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,花火一条
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他是那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,受训时期都没碰到面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是招募组
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入赛特小队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,(赛特鸣神大尉)\N我是赛特鸣神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：放电)\N从今天起就是你们的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如你们所知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天起我们就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle Arms System 简称SAS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,互相共享超脑力一同战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请新成员自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,顺带一提 我的超脑力是放电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(花火一条少尉)\N我是花火一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：点火)\N超脑力是点火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,(那歧卡门上等兵)\N我是那歧卡门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：空气操作)\N超脑力是空气操作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,加入怪伐军是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,(结人皇上等兵)\N我是结人皇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：念力)\N超脑力是念力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候 曾被怪伐军救过一命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽我所能的报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现任队员也自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(鸫娜札中尉)\N我是鸫娜札
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：透视)\N超脑力是透视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…我的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,透视很难表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是鼎鼎大名的结人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,早上都在报导你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,说皇家小少爷要入伍的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阳炎 你也快自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(阳炎丹伍长)\N第567届的菜鸟们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：透明化)\N我是阳炎丹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到的天才 指的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是你自称的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的队长 正经八百的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,朱雀区域上空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,确认有出现怪异的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,赛特小队 镜花小队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,提升警戒程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,队员们立即前往现场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静前往避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对怪异高射炮 已排除85%的怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其余仍在下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 我还没自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,(渡弗雷泽少尉)\N我是渡弗雷泽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：精神感应)\N超脑力是精神感应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,简单来说就是心电感应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在本部后方支持各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,赛特小队到E点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,镜花小队到F点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对付怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是赛特小队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,已确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好 让他们见识见识\N绯红守护者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 结人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在后方待机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等待支持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,刚入伍的第一天就急着送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们今天参观就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对喔 我们是志愿组
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,解决两个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,镜花小队 抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,各自移动到战斗地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,重 好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏有姊姊的辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,重好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(警告)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你去找人过来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要露出高兴的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我根本不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说了要你们等待支持
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来不及的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两人去救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 你太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,重 接着又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要成为帮助人类的怪伐军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如同那人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-那歧\N-别管我 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-痛…\N-你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧 怪异要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(直见兰德尔少尉)\N(超脑力：预知未来)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(重兰德尔少尉)\N(超脑力：念力)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,入伍当天就想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,压碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那歧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是直见救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因今天刚入伍的\N皇上等兵活跃表现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怪异顺利被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,皇上等兵 获得漂亮的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(岚诗宾大尉 超脑力：超高速)\N采访到此为止啰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是岚诗宾大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,诗宾大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请问今天的战斗成果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 非常努力了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(鲁卡崔佛斯中佐)\N入伍当天就被媒体关注
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(超脑力：瞬间移动)\N你也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁卡崔佛斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,七剑星六等勋章的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,出现在此的怪异\N杀了两名怪伐军士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我劝你们最好别看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,遗体缺少头部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 怪异会吃人脑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,吃人脑…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,此时的我们 还不了解许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原以为怪异 只是如灾害般的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 被怪异威胁的日常生活背后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有着极大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真正该被消灭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个疯狂的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至 我最不解的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,无须被命运所指使
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,相信定会被改写
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们今后 继续做着梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,朝阳正光辉灿烂 随后落下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在世界的尽头 究竟等着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,未来 灯火永恒不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在威胁我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谁为我们决定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是属于我们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,未来 你心中的灯火永恒不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,结人 入伍当天就表现活跃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,写报告书有得你受了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他虽然这么说\N但听说原本罚得更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 该怎么说你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 第一天的战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,算是合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(绯红守护者)
